<div data-tab-panel="employees" class="hidden space-y-6">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <div>
            <h2 class="font-outfit text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Quản lý Nhân viên</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Danh sách tất cả nhân viên trong hệ thống.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="relative">
                <input type="file" id="testVideoUpload" accept="video/mp4,video/avi" class="hidden" onchange="handleTestVideoSelect(event)" />
                <button onclick="document.getElementById('testVideoUpload').click()" class="bg-zinc-100 hover:bg-zinc-200 text-zinc-700 border border-zinc-200 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition shadow-sm flex items-center">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-video mr-2 text-zinc-500"></i>Chọn Video Test
                </button>
            </div>
            <button onclick="document.getElementById('addEmployeeModal').classList.remove('hidden'); document.getElementById('addEmployeeModal').classList.add('flex')" class="bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition shadow-sm flex items-center">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-plus mr-2"></i>Thêm nhân viên
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="saas-card bg-white">
        <div class="p-4 border-b border-slate-100 flex justify-between items-center bg-slate-50/50 rounded-t-2xl">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800"><i class="fa-solid fa-users text-slate-400 mr-2"></i>Danh sách nhân sự</h3>
            <div class="relative">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass absolute left-3 top-2.5 text-slate-400 text-sm"></i>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Tìm kiếm nhân viên..." class="pl-9 pr-4 py-1.5 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-100 focus:border-red-300 outline-none w-64">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-sm text-left text-slate-600">
                <thead class="text-xs uppercase bg-slate-50 text-slate-500 border-b border-slate-200">
                    <tr>
                        <th class="p-4 py-3 font-bold">Mã NV</th>
                        <th class="p-4 py-3 font-bold">Họ & Tên</th>
                        <th class="p-4 py-3 font-bold">Phòng ban</th>
                        <th class="p-4 py-3 font-bold">Tài khoản (Email)</th>
                        <th class="p-4 py-3 font-bold text-center">Thao tác</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody id="employeeListTbody">
                    <!-- Dữ liệu sẽ được load qua JS -->
                    <tr><td colspan="5" class="p-8 text-center text-slate-400">Đang tải dữ liệu...</td></tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Add Employee Modal -->
<div id="addEmployeeModal" class="hidden fixed inset-0 z-50 bg-slate-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm items-center justify-center">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-[400px] overflow-hidden">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 border-b border-slate-100">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800">Thêm Nhân Viên Mới</h3>
            <button onclick="document.getElementById('addEmployeeModal').classList.add('hidden'); document.getElementById('addEmployeeModal').classList.remove('flex')" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></button>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 space-y-4">
            <div>
                <label class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-1">Mã NV</label>
                <input type="text" id="newEmpCode" class="w-full border border-slate-200 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-100 focus:border-red-300 outline-none">
            </div>
            <div>
                <label class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-1">Họ & Tên</label>
                <input type="text" id="newEmpName" class="w-full border border-slate-200 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-100 focus:border-red-300 outline-none">
            </div>
            <div>
                <label class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-1">Tài khoản (Email Google)</label>
                <input type="email" id="newEmpEmail" class="w-full border border-slate-200 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-100 focus:border-red-300 outline-none" placeholder="nguyenvana@gmail.com">
            </div>
            <div>
                <label class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-1">Phòng ban</label>
                <input type="text" id="newEmpDept" class="w-full border border-slate-200 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-100 focus:border-red-300 outline-none">
            </div>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-amber-600 italic mt-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info mr-1"></i>Mật khẩu mặc định sẽ được cấp tự động. Nhân viên sẽ được yêu cầu đổi mật khẩu và cập nhật khuôn mặt trong lần đăng nhập đầu tiên.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 border-t border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 flex justify-end gap-2">
            <button onclick="document.getElementById('addEmployeeModal').classList.add('hidden'); document.getElementById('addEmployeeModal').classList.remove('flex')" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 rounded-lg">Hủy</button>
            <button onclick="submitNewEmployee()" class="px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold bg-red-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-red-700 shadow-sm shadow-red-600/20">Tạo mới</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
